con": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "OPPO 一加官宣老机型调价，手机全面进入涨价时代，这一策略背后有哪些考量？未来价格会回落吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "OPPO 官方发布价格调整公告，宣布将于 3 月 16 日起，对旗下部分已发售机型进行调价，包括 A 系列、 K 系列及一加在售机型，Find 系列、 Reno 系列与平板产品暂不调整。 公告显示，本次调价为面对手机关键零部件成本上升的策略性调整，目的是保障产品品质与用户体验。一加同步宣布调价，部分机型涨幅 300-500 元。 OPPO 此次调价标志着手机行业全面进入涨价周期。截至目前，小米、 vivo 、三星等主流品牌均已敲定涨价方案，老款机型普遍上调 300-800 元，3 月后发布的新品起售价涨幅普遍超 1000 元，旗舰与大存储版本涨幅更为明显。 OPPO 一加官宣老机型调价，手机全面进入涨价时代"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-19f2fca0127d873457b7e2527ba41fcd_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "158 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014722173789496566"}}, "attached_info": "CkkInuCvoIuZnslMEAMaCTExODcwMTY1OSCdjL/NBjAAOFBACXITMjAxNDcyMjE3Mzc4OTQ5NjU2NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1773281345.556841", "card_id": "Q_2013404964848949078", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美以袭击伊朗进入第 13 天，当前局势如何？有哪些值得关注的信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-904341b87588223643cc79763e30a0b5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "131 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2013404964848949078"}}, "attached_info": "CkoInuCvoIuZnslMEAMaCTExODY2MDEzNSDe9qvNBjAAOLMBQApyEzIwMTM0MDQ5NjQ4NDg5NDkwNzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1773281345.558467", "card_id": "Q_2014320952851260426", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待因腾讯技术漏洞，粉丝集体「一秒刷完电视剧」推高热度引发的「喝汤」狂欢？反映出影视行业哪些问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "用户发现腾讯视频存在异常机制：非会员点开任意剧集仅 1 秒（无需看完广告或正片），系统即自动标记 「 已看完该集 」。此漏洞被戏称为 「 开闸放水 」，网友实测 1 分钟内可刷完 6 部剧的首集，历史记录显示 「 全剧已看完 」。 「 喝汤 」 含义延伸：粉丝利用漏洞为在播剧刷热度，称为 「 蹭汤喝 」。如《玫瑰丛生》热度从日常约 2 万飙升至 22973（2026-03-08 数据），逼近平台峰值； 全网狂欢现象：话题页涌现大量幽默吐槽，如 「 内娱喝汤日 3.8」（对比 「 内娱反省日 3.6」）、 「 鹅还钱！」 、 「 预制瀑剧别卖惨 」； 平台紧急修复：程序员连夜关停漏洞，「 玫瑰丛生 」 热度被清零，引发 「 汤都不让喝 」 的抗议。 用户质疑平台热度造假，如《逐玉》被指 「 播放量与下载量对不上 」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c479e8d1a01037e809813d8347f5ded5_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "118 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2014320952851260426"}}, "attached_info": "CkoInuCvoIuZnslMEAMaCTExODY4NzUzNiDzoLnNBjAAOJsBQAtyEzIwMTQzMjA5NTI4NTEyNjA0MjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1773281345.559874", "card_id": "Q_2015307355995275406", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "25-26 赛季欧冠 1/8 决赛首回合，皇马主场 3-0 曼城，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-96dd189144399a5935da8537f9b80cac_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "104 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2015307355995275406"}}, "attached_info": "CkkInuCvoIuZnslMEAMaCTExODcxOTkyMCCczsfNBjAAOBZA